  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you're truly one with your soul. You fight together better than any old army could. You no longer require a <strong>Martial Die</strong> to activate your <em><strong>Soul Manifestation</strong></em> feature.</p><p>Additionally, when you inflict the charm or feared condition with a Taijutsu, you may spend 4 <strong>Martial Die</strong>. The taijutsu inflicts 5 ranks of the charmed or fear condition. These ranks of fear or charmed disappear at the end of their next turn and their duration cannot be extended by any means.</p><p></p>",
